      "content": "that's a good start. i'm trying to get more specific for the actual script writing though. like, for the more 'action' or 'drama' genre stuff, what are some of the more specific ways movies portray different ethnicities? like if i'm writing a scene about a crime thriller or a family drama, what are the go-to tropes for, say, Latino, Middle Eastern, or South Asian characters? just trying to get a sense of the landscape so i can subvert it.",
